OL,5, Sunscreen and ice cream sales soared in
OL,6, the UK as families prepared for the    
OL,7, record-breaking heatwave.              
OL,9,FSun care sales were up 66% and ice     
OL,10,Fcream 14% in the four weeks to 10 July,
OL,11,Fresearch firm Kantar said.             
OL,13,FIt predicts millions of pounds of extra
OL,14,Fspending on fans, paddling pools and   
OL,15,Fwater bottles as UK temperatures hit   
OL,16,Frecord highs.                          
OL,18,FBut grocery price rises are at a       
OL,19,Fnear-record 9.9%, and food bills are   
OL,20,Fset to rise by #454 this year, Kantar  
OL,21,Fsaid.                                  
